### Parameters


`binary_transaction` - string

Hex of binary transaction bytes.

### Request

``` java
curl --location --request POST 'https://bcn.getblock.io/mainnet/' 
--header 'x-api-key: YOUR-API-KEY' 
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' 
--data-raw '{"jsonrpc": "2.0",
"method": "send_transaction",
"params": {"binary_transaction": ""},
"id": "getblock.io"}'
```

###  Response

``` java
{
    "id": "getblock.io",
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "result": {
        "send_result": "broadcast"
    }
}
```
